=Generate an ESSENTIALS sermon package based on the following input.

INPUT TYPE: {{ $('Build System Prompt').item.json.input_type }}
CONTENT: {{ $('Build System Prompt').item.json.processed_content }}

Generate ONLY the following components and return as valid JSON:
{
  "title": "Sermon title",
  "big_idea": "One sentence central truth of the sermon",
  "main_points": [
    { "point": "Point 1 title", "explanation": "2-3 sentence explanation", "scripture": "Key verse" },
    { "point": "Point 2 title", "explanation": "2-3 sentence explanation", "scripture": "Key verse" },
    { "point": "Point 3 title", "explanation": "2-3 sentence explanation", "scripture": "Key verse" }
  ],
  "key_takeaways": ["Takeaway 1", "Takeaway 2", "Takeaway 3"],
  "estimated_speaking_time": "X minutes",
  "scripture_reference": "Primary passage"
}

Return ONLY the JSON object. No preamble, no markdown, no explanation.

=Generate a PREACHER sermon package based on the following input.

INPUT TYPE: {{ $('Build System Prompt').item.json.input_type }}
CONTENT: {{ $('Build System Prompt').item.json.processed_content }}

Generate ALL of the following components and return as valid JSON:
{
  "title": "Sermon title",
  "big_idea": "One sentence central truth",
  "historical_background": "2-3 paragraphs on historical and cultural context",
  "cultural_context": "1-2 paragraphs on cultural setting",
  "cross_references": [
    { "verse": "Reference", "relevance": "Why this verse connects" }
  ],
  "character_studies": [
    { "character": "Name", "lesson": "What we learn from them" }
  ],
  "main_points": [
    { "point": "Point title", "explanation": "Full paragraph", "scripture": "Key verse", "application": "Practical application" }
  ],
  "applications": ["Application 1", "Application 2", "Application 3"],
  "introduction": "Full sermon introduction (2-3 paragraphs)",
  "conclusion": "Full sermon conclusion (2 paragraphs)",
  "key_takeaways": ["Takeaway 1", "Takeaway 2", "Takeaway 3"],
  "estimated_speaking_time": "X minutes",
  "scripture_reference": "Primary passage"
}

Return ONLY the JSON object. No preamble, no markdown, no explanation.

